Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================MAIN========================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追着那只叫普库塔的小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在荒郊野外四处辗转的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢让我背黑锅 胆子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:02:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且帮忙进行普库塔捕获作战的阿梅莉亚和杰路刚帝士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然爽快地成了普库塔的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我做的小雪兔都打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪里搞错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal 悠久的沉睡森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 那边的小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死缠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我站住我就站住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 你以为我吃的苦头还不够多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没时间浪费在你们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方 要抓住普库塔先生很难啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种丧气话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起雾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起雾了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时学会这招的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你老老实实出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真吓了我一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然丢这种东西过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是同伴还是啥呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎 请不要乱动啦普库塔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你给我放手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你冷静一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会出现在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用得着说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是·秘·密·嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 还是好好注意下周围的状况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾这么浓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再仔细观察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 那边有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这城市到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四处草木丛生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房屋也被苔藓覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全感觉不到人气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为某种理由而被废弃的城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没被废弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这城市是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的故乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多该给我放手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 被讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是啥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是我的方便道具四号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四…四号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一号到三号是在说谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是你能对付得了的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不行 我们也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 能请你说明一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家的名字叫 塔夫拉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因某种原因隐藏在雾中的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每隔数月一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浓雾中会打开道路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔夫拉西亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像听过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就给我闭嘴 让人更加心烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔夫拉西亚是人称魔导都市时期的赛拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其末裔于数百年前创造的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也留下了这种传说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔夫拉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于一夜间突然消失的传说中的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失的…城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾几何时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市流行过一种叫杜兰姆病的疫病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 对于这种病根本束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏惧这种疫病蔓延的近邻国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也都没有伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一名魔导士为了拯救这座城市而来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就在这位魔导士眼前 城市消失于雾中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是这个国家 塔夫拉西亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坊间相传的 就是这样一个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家是自己将自己隐藏起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普库塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到中途为止是和这家伙说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个国家既没毁灭也没消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时确实没有治疗杜兰姆病的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家只能步上毁灭之途
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一位魔导士指明了救赎之路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是作为地下墓地而制造的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这与冥王大人所用的招数有些相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王是指那个菲布利佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只是在沉睡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说沉睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找到治疗疫病的方法前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家的人们都被施了魔法 陷入了沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时 整个国家被加上雾的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于人们的视野中隐去了身影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:09:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你说 危害这个国家的病是杜兰姆病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 其治疗法在数年前就已经找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人已经不用再畏惧疫病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么这些人还在沉睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 杜兰姆病的治疗法是找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次又变成施加这封印的魔导士下落不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 还真是好事多磨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没羞耻心的人还真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道就别乱说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人愿意帮助这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那个人伸出了援手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要找到那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家的人就能醒过来了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是像你们这样的小混混魔导士望尘莫及的伟大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小混混魔导士？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到有名的魔导士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫雷佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盲眼的贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师雷佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师雷佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会听到这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和冥王的手法有点相似也能理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的名字跳出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你该不会是知道什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 我和这个国家的过去完全没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我还有点俗事要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没和雷佐本人见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上是个怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师雷佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为传说中的贤者 盲眼的魔导士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有超群的魔力以及丰富的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救了众多民众
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还协助成立了各地魔导协会的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 他还真是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还战过他哩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是表面工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实内心只执着于治疗自己的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了稀奇古怪的试验不计任何牺牲的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这身体也是他实验的牺牲品之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被封印在其一对盲眼中的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24} 　 　 Ruby-Eye{\r}\N正是赤眼魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Shabranigdu{\r}\N沙布拉尼古都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这个国家的来由都知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你们快点出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实本不想让任何人进来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还有些事情不得不问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及那些魔导战车和光之剑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说也没什么好隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果红法师雷佐已经不在这世上了 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷佐已经不在这世上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果雷佐已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个国家的封印早该解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种封印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话 总有不方便的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 拿杖的那男人去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先灭火哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Exit Ball{\r}\N消化弾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁 这么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这里的封印都被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁 敢在王宫作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 普库塔你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了吗 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普塞尔·库鲁巴·塔法拉夏王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你吗 迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 在我的面前现身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用叫那么大声 我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷走那魔导战车的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有一位即便是那种不完美的试作品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也愿意花大价钱买下的贵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是什么来头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兽人加女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是此国王子的下场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是奇妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 对方毕竟是一国王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不先报上姓名就算师太了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是乔康达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢比那加鲁多王国的公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫欧塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 刚还说普库塔是王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下又说那个看起来很严厉的阿姨是公爵哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵是什么？很了不起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我也是王女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们比也不逊色的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对…吐槽的对方不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我终于也有点头绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些魔导战车是在这个国家制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后被那些家伙偷走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然知道那个魔导战车的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就是那个叫莉娜·因巴斯的小丫头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话先说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那东西打烂的可不是我哦 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现这种传闻本身就是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会让那些魔导战车卖不到好价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说价钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想把那些东西作为兵器贩卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是死亡商人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无聊的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是邪恶对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我阿梅莉亚·威尔·提斯拉·塞伦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将以正义之名制裁你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字 是塞伦王族吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛伦那自命清高的风潮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直就觉着令人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在向塞伦挑衅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 卢比那加鲁多和塞伦相比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家的规模可差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边啰嗦什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会原谅你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆风弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裂火球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 这魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回避一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你在那么狭窄的空间使用这个魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 刚才应该是直接命中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说那套铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Zanaffar Armor{\r}\N沙那法之铠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是未完成品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看样子还是能挡住这种程度的攻击魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在干什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也知道的 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无力之人的悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无力之人甚至没有人会施以援手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你说的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这种东西 你要舍弃这个国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在除此以外别无它法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Blam Blazer{\r}\N青魔烈弹波
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙那法唯一的天敌光之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被你带出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降低沙那法的价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用劳驾公爵亲自动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理掉他们就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在场的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的真轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就证明给你看看 事情可没那么简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要给我看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击魔法对这铠甲没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都只以自己的角度来考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要吃苦头的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的魔法中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎能对付那铠甲的也只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是擦到一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就麻烦你到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士 你该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我是迪克利斯先生他们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们处理掉 杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还是特准我收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯先生看来状态也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听我的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我确实算是你们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我可没有听命于你的必要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔康达公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 你给我等一下杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙那法不是号称无敌的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的误算是那把光之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且沙那法还远远没有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必那么不甘心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为完成的话 会比现在更值钱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 要找的东西你找到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是记录着沙那法制造方法的异界默示录抄本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请仔细看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个沙那法就能接近完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这么随便放在能让人看到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是请多多注意一下莉娜他们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们打算继续横加阻挠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就真正处理掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个人叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀者 祖马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================ED========================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这不是终点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}{\pos(861,445)}{\fscx80\fs16}あめ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴れ渡る空から 落ちるとおり涙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴朗的空中落下雨泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:10.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}流れてゆく雲に 追いつけなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:10.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}漂浮的流云无从追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}旅立ちの先には 新しい出会い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}旅途前方是新的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}でも流されてるようで 落ち着かなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.82,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}但随波逐流的感觉令人不安
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}それでも この瞬間に
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}即便如此 这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:36.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全てが　終わる　訳じゃない そうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:36.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}并非一切都已结束 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:41.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あきれる程 悩み抜いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:41.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}摆脱那些琐碎的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出ない答え 今はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}未知的答案 现在已不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:53.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ほら本当は　あきらめていない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:53.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}看吧 其实你并没放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}まだまだ行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}还能继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.76,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这不是终点
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一緒に行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与我同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}覚悟決めてね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}下定决心
