Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕咯隆咕咯隆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加一次咕咯隆咕咯隆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slayers Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fall on 奇祭！珍祭？ 把那颗球推上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话我要发飙咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕咯隆咕咯隆
